Class GameInfoMessage

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.triton.launcher.utils.message.servermessage.InfoMessage
it.polimi.ingsw.triton.launcher.utils.message.servermessage.infoMessage.GameInfoMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
Message, ServerMessage, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ExpertGameInfoMessage
public class GameInfoMessage extends InfoMessage
This message is sent by the server to communicate to the players some game information. It's used when the game mode is not expert, otherwise it's extended by ExpertGameInfoMessage.
